Package jetbrains.mps.openapi.editor.cells.optional

Interface WithCaret

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultNodeEditor.DefaultInspectorCell, EditorCell_Constant, EditorCell_Empty, EditorCell_Error, EditorCell_Indent, EditorCell_Label, EditorCell_Property, EditorCell_STHint, EditorCell_URL, ErrorNodeEditor.DefaultInspectorCell
    public interface WithCaret
    This is optional interface. Some cells may implement it in order to be recognized as caret supporting cells (textual).
